Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burgeoning metropolis of Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of those who lurk in the\Ndark underbelly of this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...some cower in the darkness itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while others seek pleasure to\Nescape the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man may very well have been\Na victim of the forces of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln response to such unusual cases,\NPolice Chief Kanzaki had...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...gathered up a group of people\Nwith unusual abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who regularly\Nrisks his life in movie stunts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in order to forget his past...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Koji Yamada is a\Nmember of that team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This loner of a man found some\Nhappiness in his friendly relations...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a female neighbor and her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's Jun Takamizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:01:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also burdened by a sordid past,\Nshe is one of the undead...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...unable to die as she exists\Nwith the darkness of her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koji was chosen as partner to Jun\Nwho has the clairvoyant ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to see the last moments of a victim's\Nlife as she climaxes during sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.91,0:01:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sex was supposed to be\Nloveless and dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Jun was mysteriously\Naroused and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...had become\Nemotionally drawn to Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the anguished soul of Koji...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who had taken the life of a\Nformer lover with his own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was closed and unyielding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, from the visions\Nas seen by Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was clearly determined that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the perpetrator of the multiple\Nmurders was not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there were no further leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, their leader, Chief Kanzaki\Nhad been monitoring the lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the team members\Nfor some unknown reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's the mysterious entity\Nthat oversees the murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Kotani, the man\Nwhich the entity possesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Koji seeks to get to the\Nroot of the first murder incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a second murder takes place\Nin his own neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of blood takes hold...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and causes Koji's abilities to\Nburst out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the perpetrator of the murders\Nmakes its appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it turns out to be a savage\Nand evil monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Able to metamorphose on his own,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koji attacks the monster\Nleading to a fierce battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Kotani lurks in the dark shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Chief Kanzaki spying\Non the subordinates...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the work of Koji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the sex murder investigation team...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,....has only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are the twins doing\Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can manage without\Ncounting on you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be in big trouble\Nunless you people power-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
