Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l could not save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Koji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.\NWow, you're pretty smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, l'm here to protect my mother.
