Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard should never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
