Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to go to work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like your father, Yuta?
